Class GameEvent

java.lang.Object
com.jeopardy.model.GameEvent
public class GameEvent extends Object
Represents a single event occurring during a Jeopardy game.

Game events are used for logging and process mining, and typically correspond to actions such as answering a question or recording a system-level activity.
